title: Futurama Season 1-7 With Subtitles Complete Series + All 4 Movie
description:
Every single Episode and Movie of Futurama. Encoded for minimum size.

Note: Episodes are arranged and grouped in seasons accroding to Wikipedia: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Futurama_episodes. If you want to watch episodes in order they aired on TV instead of DVD order you can use this link as a guide.

Info: Resolution is 632x480 for Seasons 1-2, 640x480 for 3-4, and 720x404 for the remaining episodes and movies. Audio bitrate is 64kbps AAC. Every episode contains English subtitles.

Sources:

    Seasons 1-4: DVDRip 480p
    Season 5 (Movies): Web-DL 1080p
    Seasons 6-7: BDRip 720p
